    <string name="transport_manual_pairing">Manual wireless pairing</string>
    <string name="transport_manual_step_1_title">Step 1 — Keep the TV\'s pairing screen open</string>
    <string name="transport_manual_step_1_body">On the TV, keep Wireless debugging and "Pair device with pairing code" open.</string>
    <string name="transport_manual_step_2_title">Step 2 — Copy the address and ports</string>
    <string name="transport_manual_step_2_body">Enter the TV IP and pairing port shown in the pairing window, plus the connect port shown on the main Wireless debugging screen. These two ports are usually different.</string>
    <string name="transport_manual_step_3_title">Step 3 — Enter the pairing code</string>
    <string name="transport_manual_step_3_body">Enter the current 6-digit code, then pair. If this fails, ZStream opens legacy ADB setup.</string>
